Package: geodk
Type: Package
Title: Access Danish Geospatial Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aleksander", "Bang-Larsen", , "contact@aleksanderbl.dk",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-7984-4650"))
Maintainer: Aleksander Bang-Larsen <contact@aleksanderbl.dk>
Description: This package provides access to all geospatial data provided by
    the danish agency called Klimadatastyrelsen. Under the hood it wraps the
    `{dawaR}` and `{dkdata}` packages which provide access to the agency APIs.
